Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall go…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this hill is really steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it? It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you say things like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Yuzu! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad is on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore him, Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:24.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you pay attention to guys like him,\Nit will only encourage him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:29.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How naïve. Even if you ignore me,\NI'm automatically encouraged!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:29.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My deathblow: Father's Slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Begone…to the ends of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:49.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it's only June,\Nbut it sure is hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:58.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was June 17 that day too,\Nbut what a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, someone else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I wonder if\Nshe's here to visit a grave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she's waving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! If I say\NI don't know her, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nfamiliar about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a classmate from\Nmiddle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all coming back to me!\NOh, boy! I feel so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to talk to\Nher all alone, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'll go and have\Na talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two go ahead and\Nvisit Mom's grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Karin,\Nwhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think the time for you to\Nlet go of your brother is close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?\NKarin, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:50.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did you follow me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What if a Hollow\Nappears when I'm not around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:55.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's no reason to…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:59.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean… If you're gonna follow me,\Nbe more discreet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, pardon me…\NI didn't think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really mad…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Killed..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said\Nabout your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said you've been\Nable to see spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,ever since you can remember,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, answer one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed your mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it a Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If your spiritual capabilities\Nwere such
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you were able to see souls\Nsince you were so little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Hollow that came after you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,may have killed your mother\Nby mistake–!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As far as you're concerned,\NHollows are responsible for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was never\Nanything funny about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but when you give that\Nas a reason for it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there isn't anything\Nthat's less funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you,\Nbut you're way off base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a Hollow or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed my mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:17.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When Ichigo was little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask,\Nout of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I might have found out\Nabout his secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:48.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ichigo might really be\Na hero protecting the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A h-hero, is he…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:55.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was around four\Nwhen I first met that hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:01.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He came to my dojo with\Nhair an unbelievable color,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:05.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,holding the hand of an unbelievably\Nbeautiful mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:09.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and with this unbelievably\Ngoofy grin on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was skinny and wimpy\Nand looked so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He really was a weakling…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was the first one to\Nmake him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just poked him once,\Nas a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even take ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:36.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he had been crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as he saw his mother\Nwho came to pick him up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he'd immediately break out\Ninto a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hated that about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A boy shouldn't be so happy\Nwhen he's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought,\Nlooking at his smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:56.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a wimpy mama's boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but he seemed really happy\Nlike he was having a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then…when we were nine…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… We were still nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was still a wimp,\Nalways clinging to his mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but she died…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come to school\Nfrom that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what he was doing,\Nso I went looking for him and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found him on the riverbank\Nwhere his mother had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was there with his book bag\Non his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When he got tired, he'd crouch down,\Nbut then he'd stand up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:50.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, he seemed to be\Nsearching for his mother, all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:55.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to see him like that…\NIchigo, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"I killed my mom…"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:15.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed your mother…\NWasn't it a Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:21.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to come\Nout until I called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:37.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rukia, it's pretty\Nhot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we go home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to stay near him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or we'll be too late if a Hollow\Nmakes an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you think about,\NHollow, Hollow, Hollow…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if your job is all you\Nthink about,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to lose\Nall your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Awk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:33.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm…I sure slept well… Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get nothing but these\Ntrying missions, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep them up\Nunless I get plenty of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Soul Reaper…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission…you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:04.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:11.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my… What a mean truck driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:22.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Let's switch places.\NI'll walk on the road side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:26.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing a raincoat,\Nso I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you from stuff\Nlike what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, how reliable…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But no…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you take the road-side\Nso long as you can't beat Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won a point from her last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There, you're all cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:43.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would always feel at ease…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,whenever my mother was nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I still couldn't tell\Nthe difference
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,between humans who were living\Nand those who were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Wait a minute, Mom!\N– Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I was really little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my dad told me they gave me\Nthe name "Ichigo"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which contains the meaning "to completely\Nprotect one thing you set your mind on."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that,\NI decided to protect my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what caused it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:50.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it was clear that it happened\Nas she tried to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just loved my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not only me…so did Yuzu and Karin,\Nwho were only four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad loved Mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our whole family revolved\Naround her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And she was snatched away…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from that center…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:30.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki Family Tomb\N		It's been a while, Mom…\N		Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're dead,\Nthere's no being well or not, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're all doing great – me,\NYuzu, and Ichigo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:47.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit crying, already, Yuzu.\NYou do this every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:51.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're 11 already this year,\Nwe're grownups.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:55.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know… I know that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:08.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's time now for our annual "Kurosaki Family\NHeadstone Dominoes Tournament"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A full two-and-a-half hours\Nof tombstone toppling–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:16.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go and\Nstart your life over from scratch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be some\N"wardrobe malfunctions," too…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, that shaggy guy\Nhas so much energy it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There'll even be some peeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:43.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The name Rukia Kuchiki was famous\Nback at the Soul Reaper Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Adopted into the\Nnoble Kuchiki family…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you were known as the\N 'Princess from the Rukon District.'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I'm Eikichiro Saidoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was two years ahead of you.\NYou remember me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!\NI was pretty popular too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People used to call me\N"that funny guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a few questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide it forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Stealth Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:35.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ding! Ding! Ding! Ding!\NTa-dah… You are correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fooling around!\NWhat is it you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is… Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting pretty\Nirritated over there…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They wonder why you\Nhaven't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows appear.\NOrders come in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I haven't gone back.\NThat's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you dressed\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dressed? What does it matter,\Nhow I dress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:26.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I guess you're finally\Ncoming of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide it. Don't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who's mother is said to\Nhave been killed by a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The guy with the spiked hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or, are you looking for pleasure\Nin the human world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I sew that mouth of yours shut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to be straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…doing it with a human boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you can't say it–!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:05.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. I thought that would\Nbe a good excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get an answer\Nthe superiors will be happy with,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to take you back,\Neven if I have to drag you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:20.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of\Nreturning for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:24.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it…\NI have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:42.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Spiky! You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:49.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're the one who\Nsaid it was an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Spiky…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Surrogate Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reaper…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way…\NWhat a stupid joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:17.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Rukia Kuchiki…\NThis is a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:18.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A serious crime…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:20.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. It's no fun fighting\Na dumb Gigai, but anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Spiky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:37.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Ughh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:45.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:51.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. You transformed,\Nand you're a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd tell you after attacking\Nme out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Back away! This is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have your sword.\NWhat can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going to have\Na talk with the priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That good-for-nothing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have you keep\Nme company for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the bait, the better…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heh-heh-heh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is brute strength all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:36.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:37.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close…and… Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This spiritual energy…\NIt's quite a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Seems pretty strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aargh! What?\NYou want to fight again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:57.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, now's not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your family\Nmight be in danger again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:01.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't come near!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin! Karin! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean\Nby "serious crime"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about\Nmy problems now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to save your family first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to ask me\Nanything about my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, will you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's your problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a deep…deep problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no way of asking\Nyou about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:21:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No good way of asking you without\Ntracking mud into your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:10.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ready to talk,\Ntell me about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, this is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy.\NOne hostage is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:08.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:13.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:28.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:54.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I decided…to protect…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,